---

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `HUBSPOT_TOKEN` | HubSpot private app token |
| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | Anthropic API key |
| `PORT` | Server port (default: 3000) |

---

## Endpoints

| Endpoint | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `GET /` | Health check and queue stats |
| `GET /dashboard` | Live processing dashboard |
| `GET /errors` | Permanent failure log viewer |
| `POST /enqueue` | Submit a contact job |

---

## HubSpot Properties Written

- `industry_ai_nurture_subject_line_em1` – `em10`
- `industry_ai_nurture_em1` – `em10` (HTML)
- `industry_ai_nurture_claude_text_em1` – `em9` (plain text, used for prior-email deduplication)
- `ai_email_step_status` (IN_PROGRESS / SENT / RETRY_PENDING / FAILED)

